Document: OpenXRInteractionProfileEditor
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrinteractionprofileeditor.rst
Summary: The default OpenXR interaction profile editor for generic interface editing when no custom editor is available.

This is the default OpenXR interaction profile editor that provides a generic interface for editing any interaction profile for which no custom editor has been defined.